name: Anirudh Emmadi
bio: Anirudh is a sophomore majoring in Computer Science. He is enthusiastic about bringing his ideas into reality and is really passionate about making a project that is useful and can be used by everyone on a daily basis. He likes participating in hackathons and has won 3 of them in the last year. Playing a video game (CS:GO) or watching a movie is something he likes to do in his free time.
